text: Arifurzaman Sagor is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He made his List A debut for Khelaghar Samaj Kallyan Samity in the 2016–17 Dhaka Premier Division Cricket League on 18 April 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Khelaghar Samaj Kallyan Samity cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
